  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This ERC defines a minimal interface for on-chain declaration of field element sub-ranges (\"segments\") within [EIP-4844](./eip-4844.md) blobs. A single function, `declareBlobSegment`, emits an event binding a `[startFE, endFE)` half-open range to the blob's versioned hash, allowing unambiguous sub-blob coordination across protocols. Zero storage (event-only) makes declarations ~7x cheaper than stateful alternatives.",
  "title": "Blob Space Segments"
